to show you how and why this can vary.

00:04:07.050 --> 00:04:09.130
So in this first example, we can see

00:04:09.130 --> 00:04:13.990
that we have a basket
abandonment rate of 38%

00:04:13.990 --> 00:04:17.050
so on average, 38% of the people,

00:04:17.050 --> 00:04:19.150
the sessions that have add to baskets

00:04:19.150 --> 00:04:21.500
don't result in a checkout.

00:04:21.500 --> 00:04:25.540
Now, in this example, we can
see a basket abandonment rate

00:04:25.540 --> 00:04:28.210
of 44%, and in this example

00:04:28.210 --> 00:04:31.460
a basket abandonment rate of 51%.

00:04:31.460 --> 00:04:33.230
Now we might look at this and think

00:04:33.230 --> 00:04:37.530
oh no, 51%, that is horrific.

