00:23:06.913 --> 00:23:08.863
you don't have to wait to get it perfect

00:23:08.863 --> 00:23:10.193
before you implement it.

00:23:10.193 --> 00:23:12.533
The final checkout abandonment gremlin

00:23:12.533 --> 00:23:14.253
that we're gonna squish

00:23:14.253 --> 00:23:17.523
is credit is declined, not
enough payment options.

00:23:17.523 --> 00:23:20.183
Credit cards get declined
