00:24:02.983 --> 00:24:05.383
and hunt and peck their credit card

00:24:05.383 --> 00:24:08.483
into some non-auto fill card form,

00:24:08.483 --> 00:24:11.353
you will appreciate the value of having

00:24:11.353 --> 00:24:13.363
two taps on the side of your phone

00:24:13.363 --> 00:24:14.523
to pay for something.

00:24:14.523 --> 00:24:17.553
Apple Pay and Google Pay
have changed the game.

00:24:17.553 --> 00:24:19.193
And with platforms like Stripe,

00:24:19.193 --> 00:24:24.083
promising merchants up to
2.5X increase in conversions,

00:24:24.083 --> 00:24:25.803
by using Apple Pay and Google Pay,

00:24:25.803 --> 00:24:27.983
it makes it an absolute no brainer.

00:24:27.983 --> 00:24:29.773
One final thing to touch on here

00:24:29.773 --> 00:24:32.593
is the rise of the split payment options.

00:24:32.593 --> 00:24:36.623
Klarna, Clearpay, Laybuy,
all these types of things.

00:24:36.623 --> 00:24:38.953
Really contentious and huge debt bubble

00:24:38.953 --> 00:24:41.203
that's likely to burst
all over everyone's faces

00:24:41.203 --> 00:24:43.453
at some point, but until that happens,

00:24:43.453 --> 00:24:46.203
you can use them to increase
your eCommerce conversion rate.

00:24:46.203 --> 00:24:47.863
For example, Klarna claims

00:24:47.863 --> 00:24:50.023
that instalment financing in checkout

00:24:50.023 --> 00:24:52.723
increases conversion rate by 30%

00:24:52.723 --> 00:24:55.480
